==Translingual==

===Etymology===
Acronym from English [[LOL]] for "laugh out loud", "laughing out loud", "lots of love" or "lots of laughs"

===Interjection===
'''LOL'''

# {{context|internet slang|Text messaging}} Used to express [[laughter]], literally "Laughing Out Loud", or "Laugh out Loud"
# {{context|rare}} "Lots Of Love".

